* Data Cardinality\nValidation
** Purpose
***_ Primary keys unique
***_ Transaction IDs unique
***_ Detect duplicates
** Pipeline Expectations
***_ Window function: COUNT per key
***_ Check count = 1
***_ Python @dp.expect decorator
** Materialized Views
***_ Aggregate to find duplicates
***_ GROUP BY + HAVING COUNT > 1
***_ Investigate duplicates
** Delta Lake Constraints
***_ PRIMARY KEY declaration
***_ Informational only (not enforced)
***_ Aids query optimization
***_ Documents data model
** Tip
***_ Use expectations for enforcement
***_ PK constraints for documentation
@endmindmap
